        -- x(x+1) = -k mod m.
        -- Quadratic has at most 2 roots in Field (ZMod m).
        -- Thus at most 2 solutions for x, thus at most 2 neighbors.
        -- Since cycle exists, degree is 2. So exactly 2 neighbors.
        -- So edges at m are fixed.
        -- Then apply IH on s \ {m} with modified condition (add edge between neighbors).
